Harbinger Capital Partners Master Fund I – Ltd. Insider Buy Transaction
 The insider of HRG Group Inc (NYSE:HRG)  16.69 +0.01 0.06%, Harbinger Capital Partners Master Fund I – Ltd. sold 220,552 shares of the electrical equipment & appliance & and component manufacturing’s company based on the avg market share price which is $13.0 for share. These transaction’s shares had a market value of around $2,873,704 US Dollars. This trade was pretty sizable one, so clearly it won’t go unseen. At the moment, Harbinger Capital Partners Master Fund I – Ltd. has rights to a total of 642,117 shares or 10%+ of Hrg Group Inc’s total market cap. 
